{"tid":19633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華：積極考慮參選特首","createTime":"2016-12-03T02:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T05:47:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b66bc9ac5bba64eb9028c6703000eb35e6fa8dc9","tid":19633,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"財政司司長曾俊華今日（12月3日）在商台節目中，稱積極考慮參選特首。 <br />\n<br />\n退休法官胡國興、前民建聯成員胡世全早前先後宣布參選特首，特首財政司司長曾俊華在商台節目中，被問到是否會參選行政長官，曾俊華指決定要從個人出發而非個人榮辱，如果參選對港人有利，即使會受到攻擊和其他影響，他也會積極考慮，現時要按步就班作決定。 <br />\n<br />\n曾俊華又指，有很多人問他是否參選，包括認識他的人和很多網友，都鼓勵他參選，因為社會上有撕裂，施政有困難，要改善現時情況。另外，曾俊華指亦有很多人叫他不要參選，避免受到抹黑攻擊、家人被騷擾等，大家的意見和鼓勵都出於善意，他非常感激。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-03-2016/34260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-03-2016%2F34260&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ff758fa1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-03-2016/34260</a>"},{"pid":"0d68057d1388e7df1d2ce6b6571a8ab59682af35","tid":19633,"uid":38412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位網友支持 尤其是LIHKG的朋友<br />\n我會繼續努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12200c059f7141e9770edc368626f14ba10d804f","tid":19633,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位網友支持 尤其是LIHKG的朋友<br />\n我會繼續努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de0b1e118c0733f32118f36fdb949cf7b4462fd","tid":19633,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5211695c370761ac428b8c0b6900193e0fce6e6","tid":19633,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位網友支持 尤其是LIHKG的朋友<br />\n我會繼續